title: The Steve Wilkos Show 04.22.08
description:
KEVIN&#039;S "CONFESSION"

Who&#039;s telling the truth? Kevin&#039;s been accused of some very serious charges, and the truth behind them could bring serious repercussions. His ex-wife Kim alleges that he&#039;s previously confessed to molesting an 11-year-old girl, and she&#039;s even got it on tape. Crystal, the mother of his children, also accuses Kevin of molesting his own two daughters after their shocking confession. Is Kevin the monster everyone claims, or does this story have another twist?
